author: Justin Hawkins Rides Again
description:
I was away on tour with The Darkness when Yungblud released "Hello Heaven, Hello" - the first single  from his upcoming fourth studio album. "Lovesick Lullaby" is the latest. 

To see Hello Heaven, Hello in its entirety, visit: https://youtu.be/xrZX47RbeJs?si=27rc1uEKSMXz9bIV and Lovesick Lullaby is here: ,
https://youtu.be/WfwUrz7s_Vg?si=uTgYPb1TSWdPNn01

To see more from JHRA,  join my Patreon here: http://www.patreon.com/jushawk

For Cameo messages: https://www.cameo.com/justinhawkins

The new Darkness "Dreams On Toast" is available now: https://thedarkness.lnk.to/dreamsontoast/
